@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cniciv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    v1 = ((v0 * wp.exp(tmp + 0.57)) + (wp.abs(v2 + 0.61) - (v2 + 0.84 + tmp + 0.15)))
    tmp = v1
    v2 = (0.41 + ((v2 + 0.99 + v0 + 0.03) + wp.exp(v2 + 0.31)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.80) / 0.89) - wp.abs(0.47))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.16) + 0.22) * (wp.sin(tmp + 0.91) / (v1 + 0.32 - v0 + 0.66)))
    data[tid] = v0
